Hi Tom,
If you use a U-Haul tow dolly.  Make sure to check the nylon straps  (that 
clamp the front wheels to the tow dolly) about every 50 miles for  looseness, 
and that you also use the safety chains to connect the dolly directly  to the 
front beam.
